          <Vi>Alfred (tên riêng, thường là tên nam)</Vi>
          <En>A male given name of Old English origin, meaning "elf counsel" or "wise counselor".</En>
          <Example>Alfred the Great was a 9th-century King of Wessex who defended England against Viking invasions.</Example>
